Quim Gutiérrez https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quim_Guti%C3%A9rrez 0 Joaquim Gutiérrez Ylla (born 27 March 1981) better known as Quim Gutiérrez is a Spanish actor. He won the 2006 Goya Award for Best New Actor for his performance in Azuloscurocasinegro. Quim was chosen by Givenchy Creative Director Riccardo Tisci to star in the brands Autumn/Winter 2013 Advertising Campaign Joaquim_Gutiérrez_Ylla ( born 27_March_1981 ) better_known as Quim_Gutiérrez is a_Spanish_actor .
